Author: micars
Title: [ANN] MiCars.io - Participate in the very inovating way to rent a luxury car
Body: Hi members  I've got big surprise for you.  Do you know what is the very last innovating way to rent a luxury car?  Do you want a rental car system, fast and easy, without agency and 100% payable with token?  Now it's available with MiCars and his NFC smart key.  PRE-ICO START ON 29/12 with 25% discount  http://www.micars.io/  https://www.micars.io/join-the-ico/  TWITTER  TELEGRAM  WhitePaper http://www.micars.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WhitePaper-EN.pdf  In Short Don’t spend any more time at a hire agency. With MiCars, you do everything remotely from registering as a customer to choosing your vehicle model with the corresponding insurance in addition to taking it to drive and returning it.  NFC Smart Key One hour before the hire time, you’ll get a notification on your smartphone with a virtual key to unlock your vehicle. Get the engine key from the inside of the car and enjoy your luxury town car or sedan.  100% Innovative Payment You may pay for your hired cars with MiCars Tokens, cryptocurrency issued through the ETH ERC-20 blockchain, which may be purchased in your secure area in the app. Payments by bank card are also accepted and completely secure.  Even More! MiCars simplifies your car hire all the way to the end. Return your vehicle to the departure site and conduct the inspection with your smartphone, taking photos as necessary.  Cryptocurrency Our MiCars Tokens, issued through the ETH ERC-20 blockchain allow you to pay for your hired cars via the application and will allow you to sign a long-term hire in the near future.  Luxury All our vehicles are high-end with full options, equipped with NFC technology to be unlocked using your smartphone.  App iOS & Android Soon available in January  Vehicles Mercedes Class A Mercedes GLA  AUDI A3 AUDI Q5  BMW 3 SERIES BMW X6  The steps to take in order to get your hands on your vehicle -Create your MiCars account by providing the documents mentioned  in the paragraph “SECURITY”.  -Put Tokens (ETH ERC-20 blockchain cryptocurrency) in your MiCars virtual wallet available for this purpose through the application.  The bank card payment option is usually offered.  -Choose and book your vehicle at any time by adding the insurance options of your choice. We suggest insurance based on the kilometres travelled.  -hour before your hire start time, you’ll receive a virtual key via your smartphone (through NFC technology) which will allow you to unlock your vehicle at any time.  -Open your vehicle and, inside, you’ll find the key to begin driving.  -Immediately take your vehicle to the MiCars departure station and conduct the inspection, taking photos with your smartphone as necessary.  Bonus :  Pre-ico Round I 1 Ether = 2591.3381 MCR 12/29 -> 01/05  Pre-ico Round II 1 Ether = 2429.3779 MCR 01/06 -> 01/12  ICO 1 Ether = 1941.0503 MCR 01/13 -> 02/13  https://i.imgur.com/SXdnt1C.jpg
